果(2名独立一致 confidence:95%)\n- **根本原因**: deploy_task.sh L1152がlesson.doneをlesson_checkで先行生成 + cmd_complete_gate.sh preflight_gate_flags() L702-713のelseブランチでhas_found_trueが未設定→upgrade不発\n- **影響**: 全忍者共通95件/245BLOCK(39%)。Codex55件 vs Opus40件(モデル非依存)\n- **推奨**: solution_a(先行生成廃止) + solution_d(テンプレートデフォルト変更) で65%のBLOCK対処\n\n## 要対応（殿裁定待ち案件のみ）\n（なし）\n## 将軍宛報告\n\n### 殿直接指示の全リスト（将軍照会への回答 — 完了・未完了問わず）\n- **⚠ /clear復帰のため、pre-/clear会話記憶は完全消失**\n- CMDを通さない殿の直接指示は、会話コンテキスト内にのみ存在し、ファイルに証跡が残らない\n- 陣形図・YAML・dashboard・reports・pending_decisionsを全調査したが、非CMD作業の痕跡は**一切検出できず**\n- **結論**: 証跡ベースでは非CMD直接指示の存在を確認できない。/clear前の記憶消失により、会話内のみに存在した指示は回答不能\n- **提案**: 殿に直接確認いただくのが確実。家老ペインの会話履歴(scrollback)に残っている可能性あり\n\n## 将軍宛提案（家老差し戻し）\n\n（なし）\n","encoding":"utf-8"}},"public":false,"created_at":"2026-02-08T17:23:33Z","updated_at":"2026-03-05T11:55:38Z","description":"🏯 将軍ダッシュボード","comments":0,"user":null,"comments_enabled":true,"comments_url":"https://api.github.com/gists/6eb495d917fb00ba4d4333c237a4ee0c/comments","owner":{"login":"simokitafresh","id":202653878,"node_id":"U_kgDODBRAtg","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/202653878?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/simokitafresh","html_url":"https://github.com/simokitafresh","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/simokitafresh/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/simokitafresh/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/simokitafresh/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/simokitafresh/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/simokitafresh/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/simokitafresh/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/simokitafresh/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/simokitafresh/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/simokitafresh/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"forks":[],